race.comment: ITA KEEPING (1) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at this track over 300m behind Son Of Spike (17.61) in a Grade 4/5. Was a winner the start prior. Won at her only start from this draw. Can discover winning form. LIL MISS SOPHIE (3) goes very well this course and distance starting nine times for three wins and two minors. Missed the frame latest (17.75) when fifth over 300m at this track in a Grade 5. Among the main chances. LUKE'S COAL (2) comes off an average run last start when seventh at this track over 300m behind Incredible Mouse (17.97) in a Grade 5. Key runner on best form. WEST ON HALO (7) placed last time out at this track and distance - worth considering.
